tags.description: The Goldman-Kuenz Sculpture Park opened in 1993. Today, we are one of the premier destinations for large-scale outdoor sculpture in the Midwest. We currently feature 70+ sculptures establishing the sculpture park as one of the largest in the Midwest.
tags.name: Goldman-Kuenz Sculpture Park at Cedarhurst
tags.note: The Goldman-Kuenz Sculpture Park is located within the 80+ acres of the Cedarhurst Center for the Arts Campus.
